Revision history for Perl extension roles

0.03 2018-01-31
    - when composing roles, we will attempt
      to load them in an optimistic manner
    - inspecting roles can now be done with
      the roles::DOES function.

    [DEPENDENCIES]
    - added Module::Runtime, to handle the
      loading of roles

0.02 2017-10-20
    [ NOTE ]
    - last release should be completely
      ignored, it's release should be
      consider an accident

    - use the actual MOP::Util::* API
      from the actual MOP v0.10

0.01 2017-10-16
    - initial release
